reviewText: Nope, they don't. No dogs in the kingdom of God!
Granddaughter loves this for she loves dogs. Full of meaning and alot of learning.
Have always loved the movies until recently I was unaware that a t.v series had even been made. After watching the first disk I can honestly say Love it!
Great set for the movie/series lovers! Role reprised by original actor, Dom DeLuise. Multiple discs included in set for entire first season!
